article_id:1132,category_name:News,title_name:A Summon Showcase, Springtime Spree, Is Coming Back!,image_path:,message:<div>A Summon Showcase, Springtime Spree, is returning and kicks off <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1583992800"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>Appearance rates for featured adventurers and dragons will be boosted during this showcase! Also, mana spirals will be added to adventurers Lin You and Hawk, who will both be featured!</div><div><br></div><div>See the following notification for adventurers who will be gaining mana spirals at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1583991000"></span> and their stats.</div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/1137">Adding the Mana Spiral to More Adventurers!</a></div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Note: The roster for this summon showcase does not include the new adventurers and dragons from the Paragons of Piety summon showcase, which will be live at the same time.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Availability period for featured summons:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1583992800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1584943140"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at some of the featured adventurers and dragons below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurer:</div><div>
